The '''Slovakia national under-18 football team''', controlled by the [[Slovak Football Association]], is [[Slovakia]]'s national under 18 football team and is considered to be a feeder team for the [[Slovakia national under-19 football team|Slovakia U19 team]].


== Current squad ==
The following players have been called up for [[Tournament|Niigata Cup (Japan)]] against Mexico U-18 on 16 July 2011.<br>

